<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <meta name="author" content="Anthony Robustelli - Z23478142" />
        <!-- Boostrap CSS -->
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <!-- Boostrap JS -->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <!-- Font Awesome Icons -->
        <link href="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.1.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <!-- Custom CSS -->
        <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <title>IMDB API Web App</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a href="#" class="navbar-brand">IMDB API App</a>
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggler" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarCollapse">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div id="navbarCollapse" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                    <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                            <a href="#" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">Profile</a>
                            <div class="dropdown-menu">
                                <p class="dropdown-item" id="profile-name">{Name}<p>
                                <p class="dropdown-item" id="profile-id">{user_id}</p>
                                <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>
                                <a href="" class="dropdown-item">Watchlist</a>
                                <a href="" class="dropdown-item" id="logout-btn">Logout</a>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>  
        <div class="main p-0">
            <div class="center-content ">
                <h4>Instructions:</h4>
                <p>This web applicaiton with leverage the IMDB API to allow users to search their favorite movie titles.</p>
                <p>Users will also be able to save titles to their watchlist which will be saved to their logged in account.</p>
                <p>Logging out and in to the account will save the watchlist of the user for later use.</p>
                <p>User information and watchlist are saved within a local MongoDB database.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="login-form" class="center-content " style="display: block;">
                <h3>User Login</h3>
                <form action="/auth">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email</label>
                        <input id="email-input" name="email" type="email" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="password">Password</label>
                        <input id="password-input" name="password" type="password" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    <button type="submit" id="login-btn" class="btn btn-primary">Login</button>
                </form>
                <br />
                <button id="signup-btn" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</button>
            </div>
            <div id="register-form" class="center-content " style="display: none;">
                <h3>Register A New User</h3>
                <form action="/auth" method="POST">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="remail">Email</label>
                        <input id="remail-input" name="remail" type="email" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="rname">Username</label>
                        <input id="rname-input" name="rname" type="text" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="rpassword">Password</label>
                        <input id="rpassword-input" name="rpassword" type="password" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="cpassword">Confirm Password</label>
                        <input id="rcpassword-input" name="rcpassword" type="password" class="form-control">
                    </div>
                    <div id="match-check"></div>
                    <br />
                    <button type="submit" id="register-btn" class="btn btn-primary" disabled="true">Register</button>
                </form>
                <br />
                <button id="cancel-btn" class="btn btn-danger">Cancel</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Custom js -->
        <script type="module" src="js/index.js"></script>
    </body>
    <footer class="fixed-bottom bg-secondary text-white">
        <h4 class="text-center">Anthony Robustelli - Z23478142</h4>
    </footer>
</html>